{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSInteger","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSInteger","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"badge","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"badge","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The current application badge number (0 to clear badge)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Reports the current badge count to Pushwoosh for analytics and to enable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"badge-based segmentation. This is useful for:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Analytics","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Track user engagement through unread counts"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Segmentation"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Target users with high\/low badge counts"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Badge management","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Allow server-side badge manipulation"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Call this method whenever you update the app badge to keep Pushwoosh in sync.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sync badge with Pushwoosh when updating unread counts:"}]},{"code":["class NotificationBadgeManager {","","    private(set) var unreadCount: Int = 0 {","        didSet {","            updateBadge()","        }","    }","","    func markAsRead(_ notificationIds: [String]) {","        unreadCount = max(0, unreadCount - notificationIds.count)","    }","","    func handleNewNotification() {","        unreadCount += 1","    }","","    func clearAll() {","        unreadCount = 0","    }","","    private func updateBadge() {","        \/\/ Update system badge","        if #available(iOS 16.0, *) {","            UNUserNotificationCenter.current().setBadgeCount(unreadCount)","        } else {","            UIApplication.shared.applicationIconBadgeNumber = unreadCount","        }","","        \/\/ Sync with Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(unreadCount)","    }","}","","\/\/ Usage in AppDelegate","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func applicationDidBecomeActive(_ application: UIApplication) {","        \/\/ Sync current badge state when app becomes active","        let currentBadge = application.applicationIconBadgeNumber","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(currentBadge)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendbadges:"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendBadges:"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"sendBadges:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)sendBadges:","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Synchronizes the application badge number with Pushwoosh servers.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/sendBadges:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendbadges:","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Synchronizes the application badge number with Pushwoosh servers."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendBadges:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"}],"title":"sendBadges:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"}}}